Crafting Recipe
1. ModRecipeProvider
    * Line 35 - List all Blocks/Items able to be Smelted/Blasted
    * Line 40 - Can Edit Smelting Time/XP/Product
    * line 43 - Same as Smelting but Blasting
    * Line 52 - Shapeless Recipes
    * Line 63 - Turn Block into 9 Items
    * Line 72 - WARNING: If Multiple Recipe Have the Same output, id: Tag is Required to Differentiate between them
            * Use Shaped() Instead of Shapeless() for Specific Positions, Because Shapeless Ignores Spaces while Shaped Doesn't
            * Must Define Multiple Letters (Line 56) for a Multi-Item Crafting Recipe

